{"title":"山里的小花","authors":["钱启贤"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":6,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山里的小花（三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱启贤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采茶女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静悄悄，雾蒙蒙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶山醒来是黎明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿云里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘着花头巾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百鸟齐欢唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山起回音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要数那阳雀嗓门高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更喜画眉换新韵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采完一山又一岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露水湿衣襟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶篓沉甸甸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篮里装满春……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筏工晚炊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江湾里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚霞染紫烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筏工晚炊时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篝火红一江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水面上，饭菜香；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上下，月一双……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金银花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在竹篱畔生儿育女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在山脚下生存安家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰霜中茎叶青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雪里发花芽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默无闻的生长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处都能把根扎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年开出金银花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把浓郁的馨香悄悄散发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的精神是何等富有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都是山里的小花……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}